---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Terms of Use" lang="en" description="NiQuit Terms of Use">
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-16" style="color:#D0D8E8; line-height:1.8;">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2" style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; color:#F5F7FA;">
      Terms of Use
    </h1>
    <p class="text-sm mb-10" style="color:#B0B8C8;">Last updated: July 4, 2026</p>

    <p class="mb-6">By using NiQuit, you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the app.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-10 mb-3" style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; color:#F5F7FA;">The app</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">NiQuit is a free nicotine cessation support app. It is not a medical service and does not replace professional healthcare advice. If you have health concerns related to quitting nicotine, consult a doctor.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-10 mb-3" style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; color:#F5F7FA;">Voluntary support</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">The app is free to use. Any donation is voluntary and supports ongoing development. Donations are non-refundable once processed.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-10 mb-3" style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; color:#F5F7FA;">Your data</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">Your personal data is stored on your device. See our <a href="/privacy" style="color:#22D3EE;">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-10 mb-3" style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; color:#F5F7FA;">Acceptable use</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">You agree not to reverse-engineer, copy, or misuse any part of the app or its content.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-10 mb-3" style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; color:#F5F7FA;">Changes</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">We may update these terms. Continued use of the app after changes means you accept the new terms.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-10 mb-3" style="font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; color:#F5F7FA;">Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions: <a href="mailto:hello@niquit.app" style="color:#22D3EE;">hello@niquit.app</a></p>
  </article>
</Base>
